# Yogkit Project Structure Guide

## Project Overview
This is a Yoga studio management system with two main components:
1. **Frontend**: Angular application in `/Yogkit/` directory
2. **Backend**: Node.js admin backend in `/yogkit-admin-backend/` directory

## Frontend Structure (`/Yogkit/`)
- **Main Entry**: [src/main.ts](mdc:Yogkit/src/main.ts)
- **App Module**: [src/app/app.module.ts](mdc:Yogkit/src/app/app.module.ts)
- **Configuration**: [src/schedule-config.json](mdc:Yogkit/src/schedule-config.json) - Main configuration file
- **Components**: Located in `src/app/modules/components/`
  - Home View: [src/app/modules/components/home-view/](mdc:Yogkit/src/app/modules/components/home-view/)
  - Navigation: [src/app/modules/components/navbar/](mdc:Yogkit/src/app/modules/components/navbar/)
  - Footer: [src/app/modules/components/footer/](mdc:Yogkit/src/app/modules/components/footer/)
- **Assets**: [src/assets/](mdc:Yogkit/src/assets/) - Images, CSS, JS files
- **Styles**: [src/styles.scss](mdc:Yogkit/src/styles.scss) - Global styles

## Backend Structure (`/yogkit-admin-backend/`)
- **Main Entry**: [server.js](mdc:yogkit-admin-backend/server.js)
- **Configuration Management**: [config/config-manager.js](mdc:yogkit-admin-backend/config/config-manager.js)
- **Default Config**: [config/default-config.json](mdc:yogkit-admin-backend/config/default-config.json)
- **API Routes**: [routes/](mdc:yogkit-admin-backend/routes/) directory
- **Middleware**: [middleware/](mdc:yogkit-admin-backend/middleware/) directory
- **Utilities**: [utils/](mdc:yogkit-admin-backend/utils/) directory
- **Admin UI**: [public/config-editor.html](mdc:yogkit-admin-backend/public/config-editor.html)

## Key Configuration Structure
The configuration follows this schema (based on schedule-config.json):
```json
{
  "banner": { "title", "subtitle", "ctaButton" },
  "header": { "title", "subtitle" },
  "schedule": { "title", "description", "batches": { "morning", "evening" } },
  "classInfo": { "title", "details": [] },
  "currentClasses": [],
  "modal": { "title", "subtitle", "form", "submitButton", "messages" }
}
```

## Development Workflow
1. **Configuration Changes**: Use the admin backend at `http://localhost:3001/config-editor`
2. **Frontend Development**: Angular app runs on default Angular port
3. **Backend Development**: Node.js server runs on port 3001
4. **Memory Issues**: Use `NODE_OPTIONS="--max-old-space-size=4096"` for backend if needed
